# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:16
translate spanish juliana4_d02ca892:

    # "I walk into the café. It's a little later than when I usually come here, and I think the place is going to close soon."
    "Entro en la cafetería. Es un poco más tarde de lo que suelo venir aquí, y creo que el local va a cerrar pronto."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:17
translate spanish juliana4_35e32b99:

    # "There's nobody inside, except for Juliana at the counter and a single customer who is standing in front of her, yelling at her face."
    "No hay nadie dentro, excepto Juliana en la barra y un único cliente que está de pie frente a ella, gritándole a la cara."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:20
translate spanish juliana4_c75e9409:

    # "Man" "You mixed the mocha syrup into the espresso!"
    "Man" "¡Has mezclado el sirope de moca con el espresso!"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:21
translate spanish juliana4_cb1b0154:

    # "Man" "I didn't want it mixed in! I wanted it on top!"
    "Man" "¡No quería que lo mezclaras! ¡Lo quería por encima!"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:22
translate spanish juliana4_a8b6a501:

    # "Man" "Do you even know how to make a coffee? Are you even capable of doing your job?"
    "Man" "¿Sabes siquiera cómo se hace un café? ¿Eres capaz de hacer tu trabajo?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:23
translate spanish juliana4_0cec673e:

    # bn "I'm sorry, sir, I'll make you another one the way you'd like."
    bn "Lo siento, señor, le prepararé otro tal y como le gusta."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:24
translate spanish juliana4_8e62b6b2:

    # "Man" "That's not good enough!"
    "Man" "¡Eso no es suficiente!"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:25
translate spanish juliana4_8255f9dd:

    # "Man" "I'm a busy man! I don't have time to stand around here and wait for you to make another coffee!"
    "Man" "¡Soy un hombre ocupado! ¡No tengo tiempo para quedarme aquí esperando a que me prepares otro café!"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:26
translate spanish juliana4_05baa30f:

    # "Man" "You'd probably fuck that one up too!"
    "Man" "¡Seguramente también lo joderías!"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:27
translate spanish juliana4_fdf235ad:

    # "I can't just stand here and listen to him talk to her like that."
    "No puedo quedarme aquí parado escuchando cómo le habla así."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:28
translate spanish juliana4_89af28b7:

    # pc "You need to step back, sir."
    pc "Tiene que retroceder, señor."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:31
translate spanish juliana4_5ade671e:

    # "Man" "What?"
    "Man" "¿Qué?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:32
translate spanish juliana4_88f0dd65:

    # "Man" "Who the fuck are you?"
    "Man" "¿Quién coño eres tú?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:33
translate spanish juliana4_d44d5f64:

    # pc "Just another customer. No need to talk to her that way."
    pc "Solo otro cliente. No hay necesidad de hablarle así."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:34
translate spanish juliana4_cc76871d:

    # pc "She said that she's willing to fix the problem, take it or leave it."
    pc "Ella ha dicho que está dispuesta a solucionar el problema, lo tomas o lo dejas."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:35
translate spanish juliana4_8f1d74b6:

    # "Man" "Look, you fucking guy, why don't you mind your own business?"
    "Man" "Mira, jodido, ¿por qué no te metes en tus asuntos?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:36
translate spanish juliana4_833654ad:

    # "Man" "You don't get to walk up to me and get in my face."
    "Man" "No puedes venir a ponerte en mi cara."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:37
translate spanish juliana4_cc19e308:

    # "Man" "I'll knock the fuck out of you."
    "Man" "Te voy a dar una paliza de cojones."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:38
translate spanish juliana4_e05676a5:

    # pc "Throw a punch then, but you're not going to like how that ends for you."
    pc "Pues dale un puñetazo, pero no te va a gustar cómo te va a salir."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:39
translate spanish juliana4_59dcf41b:

    # "Man" "Oh yeah?"
    "Man" "¿Ah, sí?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:40
translate spanish juliana4_83b8fad5:

    # pc "Please do it. There's cameras all over this place."
    pc "Adelante, hazlo. Hay cámaras por todo el local."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:41
translate spanish juliana4_effc5356:

    # pc "You throw one punch at me and that gives me all the reason I need to knock you the fuck out."
    pc "Si me das un puñetazo, eso me da toda la razón que necesito para dejarte fuera de combate."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:42
translate spanish juliana4_cc4c9eee:

    # pc "So yeah. Do it. Get your ass kicked and thrown in jail over some coffee."
    pc "Así que sí. Hazlo. Deja que te den una paliza y te metan en la cárcel por un café."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:45
translate spanish juliana4_40ec0859:

    # "The man backs down, the righteous fury draining from his face and being replaced with fear."
    "El hombre da marcha atrás, la furia justiciera se desvanece de su rostro y es sustituida por el miedo."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:46
translate spanish juliana4_fe2b8751:

    # "Man" "This bitch isn't worth it."
    "Man" "Esta zorra no merece la pena."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:47
translate spanish juliana4_2295da47:

    # "Man" "Fuck the coffee. I'm leaving and I'm never coming back to this café again."
    "Man" "Que le den al café. Me voy y no volveré nunca más a esta cafetería."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:48
translate spanish juliana4_cca1e107:

    # pc "You're right about that. You're not welcome here anymore."
    pc "En eso tienes razón. Ya no eres bienvenido aquí."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:49
translate spanish juliana4_1db12a65:

    # pc "And if I catch you harassing her ever again, I'll find you somewhere where there aren't any cameras."
    pc "Y si te pillo acosándola otra vez, te encontraré en algún sitio donde no haya cámaras."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:50
translate spanish juliana4_22b2a7b5:

    # "Man" "Fuck you both!"
    "Man" "¡Que os jodan a los dos!"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:53
translate spanish juliana4_f508640c:

    # "He leaves then, slamming the door on his way out."
    "Se marcha entonces, dando un portazo al salir."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:55
translate spanish juliana4_74e148dc:

    # "As soon as he is out the door, the tears that Juliana has been holding back throughout the ordeal flood out."
    "En cuanto sale por la puerta, las lágrimas que Juliana ha estado conteniendo durante todo el calvario brotan a borbotones."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:56
translate spanish juliana4_06b1596f:

    # bn "I'm sorry. I'm just so upset."
    bn "Lo siento. Es que estoy muy alterada."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:57
translate spanish juliana4_1af6ca0d:

    # pc "It's okay. It's over now."
    pc "No pasa nada. Ya se ha acabado."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:58
translate spanish juliana4_0321926d:

    # bn "I've never had anybody be so mean to me."
    bn "Nunca nadie había sido tan cruel conmigo."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:59
translate spanish juliana4_4867b2f0:

    # bn "I'm so glad you were here."
    bn "Me alegro mucho de que estuvieras aquí."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:61
translate spanish juliana4_1431cc27:

    # bn "Thank you."
    bn "Gracias."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:62
translate spanish juliana4_5a750733:

    # pc "You're welcome. I'm sorry that you had to go through that."
    pc "De nada. Siento que hayas tenido que pasar por eso."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:63
translate spanish juliana4_95f2d967:

    # pc "He was an asshole."
    pc "Era un capullo."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:64
translate spanish juliana4_33c3e4a6:

    # bn "Are you busy? Could I ask a favor of you?"
    bn "¿Estás ocupado? ¿Podría pedirte un favor?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:65
translate spanish juliana4_ca739373:

    # pc "Sure, what do you need?"
    pc "Claro, ¿qué necesitas?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:67
translate spanish juliana4_7f85538d:

    # bn "I'm about to close up."
    bn "Estoy a punto de cerrar."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:68
translate spanish juliana4_fa809183:

    # bn "I usually just walk home from here, it's only a couple of blocks."
    bn "Normalmente vuelvo a casa andando desde aquí, solo son un par de manzanas."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:69
translate spanish juliana4_e3b3cc34:

    # bn "But I don't think I can do it tonight."
    bn "Pero no creo que pueda hacerlo esta noche."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:70
translate spanish juliana4_9aa449a8:

    # bn "Could you give me a ride?"
    bn "¿Podrías llevarme?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:71
translate spanish juliana4_4be405a5:

    # pc "No problem."
    pc "No hay problema."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:72
translate spanish juliana4_55fd6c6d:

    # bn "Thank you. I'll just get the place closed up now."
    bn "Gracias. Ahora voy a cerrar el local."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:74
translate spanish juliana4_68ad99f5:

    # "She locks the doors and starts to clean up."
    "Cierra las puertas con llave y empieza a recoger."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:75
translate spanish juliana4_c1b65ff5:

    # "I sit down in one of the chairs and wait for her."
    "Me siento en una de las sillas y la espero."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:76
translate spanish juliana4_90065028:

    # "When she finishes cleaning and putting everything away, she comes out with a drink in her hand."
    "Cuando termina de limpiar y de guardar todo, sale con una bebida en la mano."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:78
translate spanish juliana4_26310dbb:

    # bn "Vanilla latte right?"
    bn "Un café con leche de vainilla, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:79
translate spanish juliana4_0ce9e5be:

    # pc "You got it. Thank you."
    pc "Exacto. Gracias."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:81
translate spanish juliana4_41cb1b7a:

    # bn "It's the least I could do."
    bn "Es lo menos que puedo hacer."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:86
translate spanish juliana4_8632d269:

    # "We walk out to my car together and quickly leave the café."
    "Salimos juntos hacia mi coche y nos alejamos rápidamente de la cafetería."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:87
translate spanish juliana4_f37f2114:

    # "She doesn't talk much on the way, except to point me towards her house."
    "Ella no habla mucho por el camino, salvo para indicarme dónde está su casa."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:90
translate spanish juliana4_685d057c:

    # "It's a small two-story house, without much of a yard, and no cars parked in front."
    "Es una casa pequeña de dos plantas, sin mucho jardín y sin coches aparcados delante."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:91
translate spanish juliana4_e6e6c6f7:

    # pc "Want me to walk you up to the door?"
    pc "¿Quieres que te acompañe hasta la puerta?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:92
translate spanish juliana4_d340a7d8:

    # bn "Yes please."
    bn "Sí, por favor."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:95
translate spanish juliana4_d7babbe1:

    # bn "Do you, uh, want to come inside?"
    bn "¿Quieres... entrar?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:100
translate spanish juliana4_352ba7de:

    # bn "Oh okay."
    bn "Ah, vale."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:101
translate spanish juliana4_8ad3deb0:

    # bn "Goodnight then. And thank you again."
    bn "Buenas noches, entonces. Y gracias de nuevo."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:102
translate spanish juliana4_ad22b7ba:

    # "She went inside the house and I headed back to my car."
    "Ella entró en la casa y yo volví a mi coche."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:103
translate spanish juliana4_647112e1:

    # "I could have gone inside with her and that might have led to other things."
    "Podría haber entrado con ella y eso podría haber llevado a otras cosas."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:104
translate spanish juliana4_b43224db:

    # "But I wasn't very interested in Juliana in that way."
    "Pero no me interesaba mucho Juliana en ese sentido."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:105
translate spanish juliana4_74079974:

    # "I hope I didn't hurt her feelings."
    "Espero no haber herido sus sentimientos."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:110
translate spanish juliana4_a9d6c34f:

    # bn "Okay. I live here with my grandmother."
    bn "Vale. Vivo aquí con mi abuela."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:111
translate spanish juliana4_01c04cfc:

    # bn "She's probably already asleep, so we have to be quiet."
    bn "Probablemente ya esté dormida, así que tenemos que hacer silencio."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:112
translate spanish juliana4_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "Vale."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:115
translate spanish juliana4_b5b3d01e:

    # "I follow her inside the house and up a narrow set of stairs to the right to the second floor, which is split between a bathroom and her bedroom."
    "La sigo dentro de la casa y subimos por una estrecha escalera a la derecha hasta el segundo piso, que está dividido entre un baño y su dormitorio."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:119
translate spanish juliana4_db649f95:

    # bn "So, this is my bedroom."
    bn "Bueno, este es mi dormitorio."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:120
translate spanish juliana4_1584df18:

    # bn "You're the first boy that's ever been in it, so congratulations for that."
    bn "Eres el primer chico que ha estado aquí, así que enhorabuena por eso."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:124
translate spanish juliana4_a79e5f3a:

    # bn "No, I've never had a real boyfriend."
    bn "No, nunca he tenido un novio de verdad."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:129
translate spanish juliana4_85bae903:

    # bn "Uh, I don't really want to talk about that."
    bn "Eh, la verdad es que no quiero hablar de eso."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:130
translate spanish juliana4_9b761d73:

    # pc "Okay, no problem."
    pc "Vale, no hay problema."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:131
translate spanish juliana4_3c72bdc5:

    # bn "Will you sit on the bed next to me?"
    bn "¿Te sientas en la cama a mi lado?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:132
translate spanish juliana4_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:135
translate spanish juliana4_eb8d6c3f:

    # "I sit down on the bed and she stares at me."
    "Me siento en la cama y ella me mira fijamente."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:136
translate spanish juliana4_0ec998e1:

    # "It seems like she's thinking really hard about doing something, building up the courage."
    "Parece que está pensando mucho en hacer algo, armándose de valor."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:137
translate spanish juliana4_e2bbad47:

    # bn "Do you want to, um..."
    bn "¿Quieres, eh..."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:138
translate spanish juliana4_9ceb9e90:

    # bn "Kiss me?"
    bn "¿Besarme?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:146
translate spanish juliana4_fc3f32c0:

    # bn "Oh, I'm sorry."
    bn "Oh, lo siento."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:147
translate spanish juliana4_779a0c95:

    # bn "I shouldn't have invited you up here."
    bn "No debería haberte invitado a subir aquí."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:148
translate spanish juliana4_bbbc2ff6:

    # bn "You should go."
    bn "Deberías irte."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:151
translate spanish juliana4_0c5a97ab:

    # "She quickly rushes me out of the house and closes the door. I walk back to my car."
    "Me echa rápidamente de la casa y cierra la puerta. Vuelvo a mi coche."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:152
translate spanish juliana4_e8fd1483:

    # "I just am not interested in Juliana that way."
    "Es que no me interesa Juliana de esa manera."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:153
translate spanish juliana4_ff86ea31:

    # "I hope I hadn't hurt her feelings too bad though."
    "Espero no haber herido demasiado sus sentimientos."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:160
translate spanish juliana4_64ca4f32:

    # "I lean in slowly until our lips touch, trying to be gentle with her."
    "Me inclino lentamente hasta que nuestros labios se tocan, intentando ser delicado con ella."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:161
translate spanish juliana4_06ec2189:

    # "She seems nervous and hesitant, but her lips part for me."
    "Parece nerviosa y vacilante, pero abre los labios para mí."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:162
translate spanish juliana4_8964ecc3:

    # "I can feel her trembling slightly."
    "Puedo sentir cómo tiembla ligeramente."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:165
translate spanish juliana4_3bd6817a:

    # "Then she starts kissing back with more enthusiasm."
    "Entonces empieza a devolverme el beso con más entusiasmo."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:166
translate spanish juliana4_4e52a492:

    # "She's obviously inexperienced. She doesn't seem to know which way to move her head, or what to do with her tongue."
    "Es obvio que no tiene experiencia. No parece saber hacia dónde mover la cabeza ni qué hacer con la lengua."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:167
translate spanish juliana4_7d92e450:

    # "But I can tell that she wants it really bad and she's a quick learner."
    "Pero se nota que lo desea con todas sus fuerzas y que aprende rápido."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:170
translate spanish juliana4_6627d58f:

    # "Finally, she pulls away with a smile."
    "Al final, se separa de mí con una sonrisa."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:171
translate spanish juliana4_c359a46d:

    # bn "Does this mean that you're my boyfriend now?"
    bn "¿Esto significa que ahora eres mi novio?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:174
translate spanish juliana4_5eca43eb:

    # bn "I've never had a boyfriend."
    bn "Nunca he tenido novio."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:175
translate spanish juliana4_ba5a3851:

    # bn "I'm looking forward to discovering what that is like."
    bn "Tengo muchas ganas de descubrir cómo es eso."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:177
translate spanish juliana4_9fe2e77f:

    # pc "We can have fun together, but I'm still going to be dating other girls too."
    pc "Podemos divertirnos juntos, pero yo seguiré saliendo con otras chicas también."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:178
translate spanish juliana4_a4617892:

    # bn "Oh that's fine, I don't care about that."
    bn "Oh, no pasa nada, eso no me importa."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:179
translate spanish juliana4_a7314b28:

    # bn "I'm just excited to discover something new with you."
    bn "Solo estoy emocionada por descubrir algo nuevo contigo."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:181
translate spanish juliana4_d3adbceb:

    # bn "Oh okay. I thought that meant that you were dating then."
    bn "Oh, vale. Pensaba que eso significaba que estabas saliendo con alguien."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:182
translate spanish juliana4_bc6dc91c:

    # pc "No, it's okay to just kiss because it feels good. You don't have to be in a relationship."
    pc "No, está bien simplemente besarse porque se siente bien. No hace falta tener una relación."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:183
translate spanish juliana4_64d40c0d:

    # bn "Oh, that's interesting."
    bn "Oh, qué interesante."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:184
translate spanish juliana4_9eb57aef:

    # bn "I'm excited to discover these new things with you."
    bn "Me hace ilusión descubrir estas cosas nuevas contigo."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:185
translate spanish juliana4_5fd39a0b:

    # pc "Do you want to go on a date sometime then?"
    pc "¿Quieres que quedemos alguna vez, entonces?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:186
translate spanish juliana4_1d01d15e:

    # bn "I'd love to."
    bn "Me encantaría."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:187
translate spanish juliana4_f0463399:

    # bn "But give me a little time."
    bn "Pero dame un poco de tiempo."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:188
translate spanish juliana4_e2a39d77:

    # bn "This is all very new to me, I have to take it slow."
    bn "Todo esto es muy nuevo para mí, tengo que ir poco a poco."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:189
translate spanish juliana4_fe333677:

    # bn "I'll let you know when I'm ready."
    bn "Te diré cuando esté lista."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:190
translate spanish juliana4_f2a25528:

    # pc "That's fine. No hurry."
    pc "No pasa nada. No hay prisa."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:191
translate spanish juliana4_7767853c:

    # bn "Thank you, [pcname]."
    bn "Gracias, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana4.rpy:195
translate spanish juliana4_708f41ce:

